Interactive Methods</h1></center>

<center>
<h2>
Worksheet Method</h2></center>

<ul>
<li>
Brings up a Java applet that implements the technique</li>

<li>
Allows user to adjust parameters and immediately see the impact of the
changes</li>

<li>
Worksheets can guide the user to make certain explorations</li>

<li>
Source code is available to view how the technique was implemented</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>
